data.text:
Note

# Made from NexLand Ceramic Seiko Center.

# The blades of the Ultra-Sharp series are very fragile and prone to chipping.

# The Ultra-Sharp, not so called safe blade or finger friendly... (Under standardized use, the sharper the knife, the safer it is)

# Do not break or fold this ceramic blade.

The advanced ceramic product has gradually entered personal business activities in recent years.

For example: it was applied in

# Stretched wrap / film (They are soft and tough)

# Duct tape: (There are also rich grid lines in this sticky rubber)

# Polymer fiber material Kevlar rope, paracord, fishing line, etc.

Other such as: In packaging, industrial foam and carton cutting Neoprene cutting ...

SPEC

Handle Material: ABS plastic（Metal Free）

Blade Material: Zirconia Ceramic

Series: Ultra-sharp

Blade: 20 degrees Edged

Knife Model: UK1-90

Blade Model: UB1-90-30 / UB1-90-60 (snap-off)

Size: 145*25*10mm Weight: 18g
